org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode

Class LibraryGridNavigation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.LibraryGridNavigation

  • public class LibraryGridNavigation
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Beep Patrol

    This library contains the grid navigation program, which utilizes a virtual grid with origin (0, 0) starting the center of the field. The angle fo 0 degrees begins on the positive X axis and moves counterclockwise
